divs: sighting details the witness stated in his e-mail to me : "i was drivinig south to tonganoxie from leavenworth today on county road 5, and to the right in a field was a large triangle which looked like it might have been burnt into a field. it had an arch at the back of the triangle and came to a point after about 70 feet. i found a picture on coasttocoastam.com that resembles the shape from the field. http:\\www.coasttocoastam.com\gen\page1960.html?theme=light i'm not sure if the craft described made the mark that i saw, but i can't imagine what would have actually made it."
Summary: Triangle Burn Pattern On Ground In Field
